			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
					
						
<img src="/content/dam/arts/people/julia-spaniol.jpg" alt="Profile: Julia Spaniol"/>



   
					
				</div>
				<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8">
				
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p><strong>Dr. Julia Spaniol</strong><span> conducts research that explores the impact of aging on both contextual decisions, such as the timing of an event, and on decision-making. As these thought processes decrease when people get older, motivational and emotional capacities tend to stabilize or improve with age. Spaniol investigates how motivation and reward can affect cognition throughout a lifespan and how maximizing the cognitive strengths of older adults could help to counterbalance cognitive deficits.</span></p>
</div>  
						    
					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div> 
		
