						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>The creation of a new research chair in the study and advancement of democracy was made possible thanks to a generous donation from The Jarislowsky Foundation. The $2-million gift, which will be matched by Ryerson University, will endow a chair in the Faculty of Arts that will position Ryerson at the forefront of teaching, research and knowledge exchange on democracy, and provide a public forum for discussion and debate about democracy at this critical moment in its evolution. <strong>Dr.&nbsp;Sanjay Ruparelia</strong> currently serves as Jarislowsky Democracy Chair.&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/arts/news-events/2018/09/sanjay-ruparelia-named-jarislowsky-democracy-chair/">Learn more</a></p>
